                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/8121" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">OB-0377</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2329 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">草木蔓发，春山可望:中福刘平山企业家精神的精进与远航</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Grass and Trees are Blooming, and Spring Mountains Are in Sight: The Diligence and Voyage of Liu Pingshan&#39;s Entrepreneurial Spirit in ZHONGFU</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">坚瑞，王丹，陈燕敏，廖林娟</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">福建农林大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中福海峡（平潭）发展股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大中型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">13 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业家精神；组织韧性；领导力理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Entrepreneurship; Leadership theory; Organizational resilience; ZHONGFU</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业家精神作为中国共产党人精神谱系的重要组成部分，是构筑企业核心竞争力的重要来源，也是加快建设世界一流企业的关键力量。中福平潭（海峡）发展股份有限公司（以下简称中福）是一家以可持续发展战略为目标，集造林营林、林木产品加工与销售和贸易业务为一体的上市企业。本案例以企业董事长刘平山自1994年弃政从商以来经历的数次危机为主线，描述了企业家刘平山通过充分感知企业内外情境变化，整合资源，增强组织韧性，以带领中福转危为机，不断发展壮大的故事，重点突出刘平山的冒险精神、创新精神、学习精神和社会责任精神。2019年新冠疫情爆发后，刘平山更是将创新与社会责任精神展现得淋漓尽致，通过与林占熺团队合作打造“菌草家园”，助力乡村振兴，为国家可持续发展战略贡献力量。通过案例学习旨在让学生理解企业家精神的内涵与作用，引导学生思考企业家精神与领导力关系以深化对企业家精神的理解，对于探讨新时代如何弘扬企业家精神以实现企业高质量发展具有参考价值。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">As an important part of the spiritual pedigree of the Communist Party of China, entrepreneurship is an important source of the core competitiveness of enterprises and a key force to accelerate the construction of world-class enterprises. ZHONGFU STRAIT (PINGTAN) DEVELOPMENT CO., LTD. (hereinafter referred to as ZHONGFU) is a listed enterprise with sustainable development strategy as its goal, integrating afforestation and forestry, processing and sales of forest products and trade. This case takes several crises experienced by company chairman Liu Pingshan since he gave up politics and started business in 1994 as the main line. It describes the story of entrepreneur Liu Pingshan who, by fully perceiving the changes in internal and external situations, integrating resources and enhancing organizational resilience, led ZHONGFU to turn crisis into opportunity and continuously grow. It highlights the spirit of adventure, innovation, learning and social responsibility of Liu Pingshan. In the wake of the COVID-19 outbreak in 2019, Liu Pingshan demonstrated the spirit of innovation and social responsibility incisive, by cooperating with Lin Zhanxi team to create a &quot;herb home&quot; to help rural revitalization and contribute to the national strategy of sustainable development. Case study aims to make students understand the connotation and function of entrepreneurship and guide them to think about the relationship between entrepreneurship and leadership so as to deepen their understanding of entrepreneurship, which has reference value for discussing how to promote entrepreneurship in the new era to achieve high-quality development of enterprises.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,博士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《企业家精神》、《组织行为学》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业家精神；组织韧性；领导力理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024-01</td>
